INSERT INTO `Product` VALUES (50,'The Sculpted Grace Dress','the-sculpted-grace-dress','A structured A-line dress designed to enhance the silhouette with clean paneling and a refined fit. The sleeveless cut and front zip detail add a modern edge, while the flared shape brings effortless movement. Balancing elegance with contemporary design, this piece is perfect for polished daywear and elevated occasions.\r\n\r\n26604500\r\nComposition: 97% Polyester 3% Spandex\r\nDress -  Skater Length (UK 10)\r\nSolid Wooven Fabric\r\nBody Fitted\r\nSleeveless\r\nFront Zipper Detail\r\nModel height: 5’.7”\r\nModel Wearing: UK10',8390,1,'2026-04-24 11:19:03.882','2026-04-24 11:24:23.387',2),(51,'The Executive Muse Dress','the-executive-muse-dress','A refined tailored dress that blends structured elegance with soft femininity. Featuring a muted patchwork print in earthy tones, it reflects timeless sophistication with a modern edge. The clean silhouette, sharp collar, and subtle puff sleeves enhance its polished appeal. Designed for confident women, this piece offers an effortless transition from professional settings to elevated everyday wear.\r\n\r\n24609309\r\nComposition: 100% Polyester\r\nDress -  Skater Length (UK 10)\r\nElbow Sleeve\r\nPrinted Wooven Fabric\r\nBody Fitted\r\nBack Zipper Detail\r\nModel height: 5’.7”\r\nModel Wearing: UK10',8490,1,'2026-04-24 11:27:01.030','2026-04-24 11:27:13.393',2),(52,'The Crimson Grace Dress','the-crimson-grace-dress','A figure-hugging ribbed midi dress designed to enhance the natural silhouette with comfort and ease. The soft stretch fabric contours the body, while the button-down front and subtle slit add movement and detail. Finished in a rich crimson tone, this piece blends simplicity with bold femininity, making it perfect for effortless day-to-evening styling.\r\n\r\n26601200\r\nComposition: 85% Polyester 15% Spandex\r\nDress - Midi Length ( UK 10))\r\nSleeveless\r\nSolid Knitted Fabric\r\nBody Fitted\r\nFront Button Detail\r\nModel height: 5’.7”\r\nModel Wearing: UK10',7190,1,'2026-04-24 13:56:13.265','2026-04-24 13:56:13.265',2),(53,'The Soft Muse Top','the-soft-muse-top','A relaxed, tailored shirt that blends understated elegance with modern ease. Designed with a fluid silhouette and soft structure, it offers a refined yet effortless look. The minimal detailing and lightweight fabric enhance comfort while maintaining a polished finish. Perfect for versatile styling, this piece transitions seamlessly from workwear to elevated casual dressing.\r\n\r\n24631307\r\nComposition: 100% Polyester\r\nTop -  Normal Length ( UK 10)\r\nShort Sleeve\r\nSolid Woven Fabric\r\nFront Button Detail\r\nLoose Fitted\r\nModel height: 5’.7”\r\nModel Wearing: UK10',5690,1,'2026-04-24 13:58:32.130','2026-04-24 13:58:32.130',2),(54,'The Safari Belted Shirt Dress','the-safari-belted-shirt-dress','A striking fusion of bold print and classic tailoring, this shirtdress features an organic, zebra-inspired pattern in a sophisticated, earthy palette. The silhouette is defined by a sharp point collar and a tonal belt with a polished circular buckle that cinches the waist for a structured fit. With its relaxed, mid-length cut and voluminous short sleeves, this piece offers an effortless transition from professional resort wear to evening social gatherings.\r\n\r\n24633306\r\nComposition: 100% Polyester\r\nDress -Skater Length (UK 10)\r\nBody Fitted\r\nFront Button Detail\r\nPrinted Woven Fabric\r\nBelt Detail\r\nModel height: 5’.7”\r\nModel Wearing: UK10',8590,1,'2026-04-24 14:20:40.791','2026-04-24 14:20:40.791',2),(55,'The Sculpted Orbital Velt Coat','the-sculpted-orbital-velt-coat','A bold evolution of classic tailoring, this vest features a dramatic deep-scoop orbital neckline that artfully frames the torso. The structured bodice is cinched by two signature gold-tone hardware buttons, adding a touch of luxe utility to the clean-lined design. With its architectural cut and sleek, sleeveless silhouette, it serves as a versatile layering piece. Wear it over a crisp button-down for a modern professional look or alone for a sharp, minimalist statement.\r\n\r\n26601700\r\nComposition: 65% Tencil 35% Cotton \r\nBlazer - Normal Length ( UK 10)\r\nSleeveless\r\nSolid Wooven Fabric\r\nFront Button Detail\r\nModel height: 5’.7”\r\nModel Wearing: UK10',7390,1,'2026-04-24 14:41:51.579','2026-04-24 15:02:39.919',2),(56,'The Crop Kinetic Blazer','the-crop-kinetic-blazer','A sharp, contemporary take on traditional tailoring, this top features a boldly cropped hemline and structured shoulders. The design is punctuated by wide notched lapels and a secure button closure, creating a balanced silhouette that pairs effortlessly with high-waisted separates. Its clean construction and architectural minimalist appeal make it a versatile layering piece for a modern wardrobe. This blazer delivers a sophisticated, utilitarian edge that transitions seamlessly from day to evening.\r\n\r\n25617501\r\nComposition: 68% Polyester, 30% Cotton, 2% Spandex\r\nBlazer - Crop Length ( UK 10)\r\nLong Sleeve\r\nSolid Woven Fabric\r\nBody Fitted\r\nFront Button Detail\r\nModel height: 5’.7”\r\nModel Wearing: UK10',8990,1,'2026-04-24 14:45:07.785','2026-04-24 14:45:07.785',2),(57,'The Luna Embroidered WW Top','the-luna-embroidered-ww-top','The shirt features a classic pointed collar and a concealed button placket for a clean, streamlined front. It is characterized by dropped shoulders and voluminous bishop sleeves that are gathered at the cuffs. A decorative wide band of tonal embroidery and horizontal pintuck detailing wraps around the mid-sleeve, providing a sophisticated focal point. The oversized, longline hem allows it to be worn as a tunic over slim-fit bottoms or tucked in to create a more voluminous, high-fashion shape.\r\n\r\n25618600\r\nComposition: 55% Tencil 45% Cotton\r\nTop - Normal Length (UK 10) \r\nLong Sleeve\r\nLoose Fitted\r\nFront Button Detail\r\nSolid Wooven Fabric\r\nSleeve Embroidery Detail\r\nModel height: 5’.7”\r\nModel Wearing: UK10',7390,1,'2026-04-25 11:06:31.618','2026-04-25 11:06:46.526',2),(58,'The Soft Authority Skirt','the-soft-authority-skirt','A flowy midi skirt designed with delicate pleats and a soft, airy silhouette. The lightweight fabric and elasticated waist offer comfort while maintaining an elegant drape. Effortlessly feminine, this piece brings movement and grace to everyday dressing, making it perfect for both relaxed and refined styling.\r\n\r\n26606600\r\nComposition: 100% Polyester\r\nSkirt - Midi Length (UK 10)\r\nSolid Woven Fabric\r\nFull Lining\r\nWaist Band Elastic Detail\r\nModel height: 5’.7”\r\nModel Wearing: UK10',8490,1,'2026-04-25 11:08:00.250','2026-04-25 11:08:00.250',2),(59,'Bubble Bliss Dress','bubble-bliss-dress','Strappy Bubble Hem Maxi Dress featuring a soft, flowy\r\nsilhouette with a playful bubble hem finish. Designed with\r\nsmocking at the bust for a flattering, comfortable fit, it\r\nenhances shape while allowing ease of movement. Available\r\nin pastel shades, this maxi dress is perfect for both relaxed\r\nsummer days and dressing up for special occasions.\r\n\r\n26301600\r\nComposition: 55% Tencel 45% Cotton\r\nDress - Length 44 1/2\'\'- (UK 8)\r\nStrappy Back Knot Detail\r\nGold Ring & Slider Detail\r\nBubble Hem Finish Detail\r\nSolid Fabric \r\nModel height: 5’.7”\r\nModel Wearing: UK 8',12490,1,'2026-04-25 11:17:28.368','2026-04-25 11:17:28.368',3);
